dom sales figures for ''Let Go'' as of November 2011.<ref name=\"Harris\">{{cite web|url=http://jam.canoe.ca/Music/Artists/Q/Queen/2006/11/17/2391437.html |title=Queen rules \u2013 in album sales |last=Harris |first=Bill |work=Toronto Sun |date=November 17, 2011 |accessdate=October 23, 2011}}</ref>}}\n|\n* [[Canadian Recording Industry Association|MC]]: Diamond<ref name=\"MC\">{{cite web |url=https://musiccanada.com/gold-platinum/?fwp_gp_search=Avril%20Lavigne |title=Gold/Platinum: Avril Lavigne |publisher=Music Canada |accessdate=January 9, 2015}}</ref>\n* [[Australian Recording Industry Association|ARIA]]: 7\u00d7 Platinum<ref>{{cite web|title=ARIA Charts \u2013 Accreditations \u2013 2003 Albums |url=http://www.aria.com.au/pages/aria-charts-accreditations-albums-2003.htm |publisher=[[Australian Recording Industry Association]] |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120207130327/http://www.aria.com.au/pages/aria-charts-accreditations-albums-2003.htm |archivedate=February 7, 2012  }}</ref>\n* [[British Phonographic Industry|BPI]]: 6\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"BPI\">{{cite web|url=https://www.bpi.co.uk/brit-certified/ |title=Certified Awards|publisher=[[British Phonographic Industry]] |accessdate=July 18, 2014 |format=enter \"Avril Lavigne\" into the \"Keywords\" box, then select \"Search\"}}</ref>\n* [[Bundesverband Musikindustrie|BVMI]]: 3\u00d7 Gold<ref name=\"BVMI\">{{cite certification|region=Germany|artist=Avril Lavigne|type=album|accessdate=December 8, 2012}}</ref>\n* [[Federazione Industria Musicale Italiana|FIMI]]: Diamond<ref name=\"FIMI certifications\"/>\n* [[International Federation of the Phonographic Industry|IFPI]] AUT: Platinum<ref name=\"IFPIAUT\">{{cite web|url=http://www.ifpi.at/?section=goldplatin |title=Gold & Platin |publisher=[[International Federation of the Phonographic Industry]] |accessdate=April 7, 2011 |format=To access, user must enter the search parameter \"Avril Lavigne\" as Interpret}}</ref>\n* IFPI SWI: 2\u00d7 Pl