-shop/6458321/avril-lavigne-give-you-what-you-like-new-music-video|title=Avril Lavigne Teases New Music Video Following Undisclosed Illness|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|accessdate=February 3, 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Fly\"\n| Lavigne and Robb Dipple\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://imvdb.com/video/avril-lavigne/fly|title=Fly (2015) by Avril Lavigne|publisher=Imvdb.com|accessdate=April 16, 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Head Above Water\"\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2018\n| [[Elliott Lester]]\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.idolator.com/7684744/avril-lavigne-shares-pic-set-new-music-video|title=Avril Lavigne Shares Pic From The Set Of Her New Music Video|publisher=[[Idolator (website)|Idolator]]|accessdate=August 23, 2018|date=August 23, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Tell Me It's Over\"\n| Erica Silverman\n| \n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"I Fell in Love With the Devil\"\n| 2019\n| Elliott Lester\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"5\"| Guest appearances\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"[[Hundred Million]]\"\n| 2002\n| [[Treble Charger]]\n| Wendy Morgan\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://imvdb.com/video/treble-charger/hundred-million|title=Hundred Million (2002) by Treble Charger|publisher=Imvdb.com|accessdate=April 15, 2007}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Bethamphetamine (Pretty Pretty)\"\n| 2006\n| [[Butch Walker]] \n| Moh Azima \n| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/videos/butch-walker/109624/bethamphetamine-pretty-pretty.jhtml |title=Butch Walker \u203a Music Videos |publisher=MTV |accessdate=August 23, 2006 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090115110931/http://www.mtv.com/videos/butch-walker/109624/bethamphetamine-pretty-pretty.jhtml |archivedate=January 15, 2009  }}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Wavin' Flag\"\n| 2010\n| [[Young Artists for Haiti]]\n| Dave Russell \n| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/videos/young-artists-for-haiti/736527/wavin-flag.jhtml|title=Young Artists For Haiti \u203a Music Videos|publisher=MTV|