60304073452/http://nztop40.co.nz/chart/albums?chart=1233|archivedate=March 4, 2016 |accessdate=August 21, 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Under My Skin (Avril Lavigne album)|Under My Skin]]''\n|\n*Released: May 25, 2004\n*Label: Arista\n*Format: LP, CD, cassette, digital download\n| 1 || 1 || 1 || 1 || 3 || 1 || 7 || 2 || 1 || 1\n|\n* World: <!--DO NOT add 12,000,000 or other sales figures. Source says 10,000,000.-->10,000,000{{efn|group=upper-alpha|Worldwide sales figures for ''Under My Skin'' as of January 2011.<ref name=\"cmm\"/>}}\n* US: 3,200,000{{efn|group=upper-alpha|United States sales figures for ''Under My Skin'' as of September 2015.<ref name=\"ask billboard15\"/>}}\n* JPN: 924,000<!--Source says 924,000. DO NOT add other sales figures.-->{{efn|group=upper-alpha|Japan sales figures for ''Under My Skin'' as of September 2004.<ref>{{cite web|script-title=ja:\u5e74\u9593\u30a2\u30eb\u30d0\u30e0\u30d2\u30c3\u30c8\u30c1\u30e3\u30fc\u30c8 2004\u5e74(\u5e73\u621016\u5e74) |url=http://entamedata.web.fc2.com/music/music_a2004.html|publisher=Oricon|accessdate=September 19, 2004|language=Japanese}}</ref>}}\n|\n* MC: 5\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"MC\"/>\n* ARIA: Platinum<ref>{{cite web|title=ARIA Charts \u2013 Accreditations \u2013 2004 Albums |url=http://www.aria.com.au/pages/aria-charts-accreditations-albums-2004.htm |publisher=[[Australian Recording Industry Association]] |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120110090457/http://aria.com.au/pages/aria-charts-accreditations-albums-2004.htm |archivedate=January 10, 2012  }}</ref>\n* BPI: 2\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"BPI\"/>\n* BVMI: Gold<ref name=\"BVMI\"/>\n* FIMI: 3\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"FIMI certifications\"/>\n* IFPI AUT: Platinum<ref name=\"IFPIAUT\"/>\n* IFPI SWI: Platinum<ref name=\"IFPISwitzerlandCertifications\"/>\n* RIAA: 3\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"RIAA\"/>\n* RIAJ: Million<ref name=\"RIAJalbum\"/>\n* RMNZ: Gold<ref>{{cite web|title=NZ Top 40 Albums Chart \u2013 27 September 2