07Albums.htm |publisher=[[Australian Recording Industry Association]] |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120214080303/http://aria.com.au/pages/httpwww.aria.com.aupagesARIACharts-Accreditations-2007Albums.htm |archivedate=February 14, 2012  }}</ref>\n* BPI: Platinum<ref name=\"BPI\"/>\n* BVMI: Gold<ref name=\"BVMI\"/>\n* FIMI: 2\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"FIMI certifications\"/>\n* IFPI AUT: Platinum<ref name=\"IFPIAUT\"/>\n* IFPI SWI: Platinum<ref name=\"IFPISwitzerlandCertifications\"/>\n* RIAA: 2\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"RIAA\"/>\n* RIAJ: Million<ref name=\"RIAJalbum\"/>\n* RMNZ: Gold<ref>{{cite web|title=NZ Top 40 Albums Chart \u2013 10 September 2007|url=http://nztop40.co.nz/chart/albums?chart=1447|publisher=[[Recorded Music NZ]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304122522/http://nztop40.co.nz/chart/albums?chart=1447|archivedate=March 4, 2016 |accessdate=August 21, 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Goodbye Lullaby]]''\n|\n* Released: March 8, 2011\n* Label: RCA\n* Format: LP, CD, digital download\n| 2 || 1 || 3 || 4 || 5 || 2 || 7 || 2 || 9 || 4\n|\n* World: 2,000,000{{efn|group=upper-alpha|Worldwide sales figures for ''Goodbye Lullaby'' as of Octoberh 2017.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.umusicpub.com/us/Artists/A/Avril-Lavigne.aspx|title=Avril Lavigne UMPG|publisher=[[Universal Music Publishing Group]]|accessdate=October 30, 2017}}</ref>}}\n* US: 394,000<!--Source says 394,000. DO NOT add other sales figures. -->{{efn|group=upper-alpha|United States sales figures for ''Goodbye Lullaby'' as of September 2015.<ref name=\"ask billboard15\"/>}}\n* JPN: 410,000{{efn|group=upper-alpha|Japan sales figures for ''Goodbye Lullaby'' as of November 2013.<ref>{{cite web|title=Lady Gaga And Avril Lavigne's Latest Albums Sell Big In Japan|url=http://popdust.com/2013/11/13/lady-gaga-and-avril-lavigne-are-still-really-big-in-japan/|publisher=POP DUST|accessdate=November 13, 2013}}</ref>}}\n|\n* ARIA: Gold<ref>{{cite web|title=ARIA Charts 