azon.co.uk/Nissan-Live-Sets-Yahoo-Music/dp/B006NVLTHI \n |archivedate=September 10, 2014 \n}}</ref> \n* Label: RCA\n* Format: Digital download\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''MTV.com Live:<br />Avril Lavigne''\n|\n* Released: March 25, 2008<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/il/album/mtv.com-live-avril-lavigne-ep/id276082584 |title=MTV.com Live: Avril Lavigne \u2013 EP by Avril Lavigne |publisher=[[Apple Inc.|Apple]] |work=[[iTunes Store]] |accessdate=March 25, 2008 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141208022307/https://itunes.apple.com/il/album/mtv.com-live-avril-lavigne-ep/id276082584 |archivedate=December 8, 2014 |url-status=live  }}</ref>\n* Label: Arista\n* Format: Digital download\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''Control Room: Live'' \n|\n* Released: May 14, 2008<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/il/album/control-room-live-ep/id277742545 |title=Control Room (Live) \u2013 EP by Avril Lavigne |publisher=[[Apple Inc.|Apple]] |work=[[iTunes Store]] |accessdate=May 14, 2008 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141208022301/https://itunes.apple.com/il/album/control-room-live-ep/id277742545 |archivedate=December 8, 2014 |url-status=live  }}</ref>\n* Label: RCA\n* Format: Digital download\n|}\n\n==Singles==\n\n===As lead artist===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|+ List of singles, with selected chart positions and certifications\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:16em;\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Year\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"10\"| Peak chart positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:13em;\"| [[List of music recording certifications|Certifications]]\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Album\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em; font-size:90%;\"| [[Canadian Hot 100|CAN]]<br><ref name=\"CAN-Sin\">For Canadian peaks:\n* For singles from ''Let Go'': {{cite web|url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/let-go-mw0000222043/awards|title=Avril Lavigne: Let Go|publisher=Allmusic|accessdate=Ap